These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-1::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, july, december, may
There are 4 different favourite colors: orange, brown, green, light-blue
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, scrabble, billiard, bridge
 1. the person who likes green is in an odd position##4
 2. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
 3. the person playing billiard is not to the right of the person who likes orange##8
 4. the person playing mah-jongg is not the person who's birthday is in may##6
 5. the person who's birthday is in december is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in september##5
 6. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person who likes green##1
 7. the person playing billiard is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in july##8
 8. the person who's birthday is in july is not the person playing bridge##6
 9. the person who's birthday is in september is not the person who likes light-blue##6
10. the person playing scrabble is the person who likes light-blue##1
11. the person who's birthday is in july is not to the right of the person playing billiard##8
12. the person who's birthday is in july is in an even position##4
13. the person who's birthday is in may is not to the right of the person playing bridge##8
14. the person who likes green is not to the right of the person playing billiard##8

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |     2      |     3      |      4       |
| Birthday    | september         | may     | december     | july         |
| Color   | brown | light-blue    | green     | orange |
| Game   | mah-jongg       | scrabble | bridge | billiard       |

