.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-2::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, chaman, bolivar, pall-mall
The people have 4 different hobbies: skydiving, dancing, baking, filmmaking
House: ranch-style, modern, futuristic, art-deco
 1. the person who's hobby is baking is not to the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##8
 2. the bolivar-smoker is on the far left##1
 3. the futuristic house is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
 4. the pall-mall-smoker is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 5. the person who's hobby is skydiving is not the bolivar-smoker##6
 6. the ranch-style house is on the right of the siglo-smoker##1
 7. the pall-mall-smoker is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 8. the siglo-smoker is on the left of the pall-mall-smoker##1
 9. the pall-mall-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is baking##5
10. the siglo-smoker is on the right of the art-deco house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |      2      |     3      |     4      |
| Cigar   | bolivar          | siglo      | pall-mall      | chaman   |
| Hobby        | baking     | skydiving | dancing | filmmaking      |
| House      | art-deco | modern    | ranch-style  | futuristic |

