 3. the person who likes chestnut is on the right of the software-developer##1
 4. the manager is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to hannover##5
 5. the person traveling to paris is not the nurse##6
 6. the nurse is on the left of the person traveling to hannover##1
 7. the nurse is not to the right of the software-developer##8
 8. the person who likes purple is on the left of the lawyer##1
 9. the person who likes red is in an even position##4
10. the person who likes purple is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to rome##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |   3    |     4      |
