 1. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the person who growsiris##1
 2. the person driving the taxi is not to the left of the person who growsirispy##8
 3. the person who growsiris is somewhere to the right of the owner of the frog##5
 4. the owner of the frog is on the far left##1
 5. the owner of the goldfish is not to the right of the person driving the taxi##8
 6. the person driving the roller is not to the right of the owner of the turtle##8
 7. the person who growsaconite is somewhere to the left of the owner of the turtle##5
 8. the person driving the boat is somewhere to the right of the person driving the taxi##5
 9. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
10. the owner of the turtle is the person driving the roller##1
11. the person who growsdaffodil is somewhere to the right of the person who growsirispy##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |    4    |
| Pet   | frog   | turtle | goldfish    | dog |
| Flower   | aconite    | irispy     | daffodil   | iris     |
| Transport   | airplane | roller   | taxi | boat    |

