 3. the person traveling to berlin is somewhere between the person who's hobby is gardening and the person playing domino##7
 4. the person traveling to prague is not to the left of the person playing backgammon##8
 5. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##3
 6. the person traveling to berlin is the person playing mah-jongg##1
 7. the person who's hobby is cooking is somewhere to the right of the person playing billiard##5
 8. the person traveling to marseilles is between the person who's hobby is cooking and the person traveling to berlin##2
 9. the person playing domino is not to the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##8
10. the person who's hobby is camping is not to the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##8
11. the person traveling to nizza is somewhere to the left of the person playing domino##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |   3    |     4     |
