 3. the person who likes ivory is not to the left of the fan of punk##8
 4. the fan of punk is on the far left##1
 5. the person who likes blood-red is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the owner of the chinchilla is not to the left of the person who likes black##8
 7. the owner of the horse is on the left or right of the owner of the chinchilla##3
 8. the owner of the chinchilla is somewhere to the right of the person who likes blood-red##5
 9. the person who likes ivory is not to the left of the fan of metal##8
10. the fan of jazz is not to the left of the person who likes ivory##8
11. the owner of the chinchilla is not to the left of the person who likes ebony##8
12. the person who likes ivory is on the left or right of the fan of hip-hop##3
13. the owner of the chinchilla is somewhere to the left of the person who likes ivory##5
14. the person who likes ebony is on the left of the person who likes ivory##1

.:: Answer ::.
