.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-20::.
City: berlin, edinburgh, london, boston
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: october, november, december, march
4 different games are played: chess, scrabble, bridge, whist
1. the person who's birthday is in october is the person playing chess##1
2. the person traveling to edinburgh is not to the right of the person playing scrabble##8
3. the person playing whist is between the person who's birthday is in october and the person who's birthday is in march##2
4. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
5. the person traveling to edinburgh is not the person playing bridge##6
6. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1
7. the person playing bridge is somewhere between the person playing whist and the person playing scrabble##7
8. the person playing whist is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
9. the person playing bridge is the person traveling to berlin##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |    3     |     4      |
| City   | edinburgh | berlin     | boston  | london |
| Birthday           | november      | march        | december   | october |
| Game         | scrabble  | bridge | whist | chess       |

 